Abilityc back to ToC or Class ToC

IRI: http://purl.org/ontology/tetraverse/tetraversetcg/ability/ont/Ability

has super-classes
Concept c
has sub-classes
Active Ability c, Passive Ability c
is in domain of
cost op, effect op
is in range of
ability op
is also defined as
named individual

Air Orbc back to ToC or Class ToC

IRI: http://purl.org/ontology/tetraverse/tetraversetcg/item/ont/AirOrb

Can be used to evolve an anima into a higher stage air type anima.
An orb that can be consumed by an anima and used to find and place any compatible air type anima that is one stage higher.
has super-classes
Evolution Orb c
